{"tid":812782,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[大方得體] 拉莫斯:摩迪比那些靠marketing宣傳的入圍者更值得獲獎","createTime":"2018-09-10T02:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T13:16:25.000Z","uid":34571,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f7d038e17e2af169257edd7d658f710713f08eaa","tid":812782,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T02:17:18.000Z","msg":"&quot;We will see [who wins The Best],&quot; Ramos said when asked whether Modric should win ahead of fellow nominees Ronaldo and Mohamed Salah. &quot;There are few players that I am as proud of having in my team as him.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;He is a great friend and a great player. He is one of the few players who [if he wins] would make me as happy as if they had given it to me.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Maybe there are players with more marketing, with a bigger name but Modric deserves that award.&quot;"},{"pid":"dfd54b378fe4e2e3bb29751201f52bbfad966da7","tid":812782,"uid":34571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T02:18:16.000Z","msg":"&quot;Pique has been a great centre-back,&quot; Ramos said. &quot;He has given a lot to his club and the national team and he is a player who makes the difference.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;But we have to look to the future and not the past. We are grateful to what he did but there are people who can replace him.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Today Nacho has done very well. Nobody is essential, but it is true that Pique has done a splendid job.&quot;"},{"pid":"1a69ac1b94c6443d653acc2b08bb17d89187062b","tid":812782,"uid":52571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T02:47:00.000Z","msg":"講得好！幫推"},{"pid":"b54698885e71dbf1b25e213630c83366cff19ab0","tid":812782,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a69ac1b94c6443d653acc2b08bb17d89187062b","tid":812782,"uid":52571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T02:47:00.000Z","msg":"講得好！幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T0